IMAPStore       gmail-remote
Host            imap.gmail.com
Port            993
User            aarya.bhatia1678@gmail.com
PassCmd         "pass show mutt/aarya.bhatia1678@gmail.com"
SSLType         IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore    gmail-local
Path            ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox           ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders      Verbatim

Channel         gmail
Far             :gmail-remote:
Near            :gmail-local:
Create          Both
Expunge         Both
Patterns        *
SyncState       *
